      <h2>SMS operations depth 3: cost-per-message modeling including carrier…</h2>
      <p>For <strong>alternatives yotpo email sms alternative</strong>, cost-per-message modeling including carrier fees and discount depth is not optional infrastructure. Shopify SMS apps that recover urgent revenue without wrecking consent treat every text as a scarce interrupt — cart recovery after meaningful checkout intent, launch access for opted-in VIPs, replenishment when SKU usage data supports timing.</p>
